item.title: Keaton Wagler Scores 28, Leads No. 9 Illinois to 78-69 Win Over No. 5 Nebraska
item.description: Keaton Wagler scored 28 points and No. 9 Illinois won its 11th consecutive game, beating No. 5 Nebraska on Sunday, 78-69.
